  "detailed_description": "\"Fragile Love\" is the second yuri themed visual novel produced and distributed by XuWuLe<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Story-</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >This is a story about promises and redemption.<br>They were childhood inseparable playmates, but when we said goodbye, they were strangers<br>They don't like each other, but they also attract each other,<br>They are incompatible opponents of fire and water, and they are a perfect match for lovers.</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Characters-</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2773520/extras/d7bdab381e3145cb6e2c9d10e377371a.avif?t=1753181073\" width=500 height=304 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2773520/extras/b0e9cf6e478c819c4169a957b019a492.avif?t=1753181073\" width=500 height=304 /></span><br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>About-</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >着重描写女性之间的微妙细腻感情；</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >纯爱题材，唯一cp，结局的好坏取决于恋爱中的细枝末节；</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >全人物全程配音，体验声入人心的真情对白；</h2><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Staff-</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【制作】xuwule</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【企划】xuwule</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【剧本】selto</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【立绘，cg】大雾</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【背景】诗歌，jancycoco</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【配音】梧枝枝，米糊，沐月幺</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【ui】xuwule</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【pv】xuwule</h2><br>特别感谢：woctordho  鹰仓白霞",
  "about_the_game": "\"Fragile Love\" is the second yuri themed visual novel produced and distributed by XuWuLe<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Story-</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >This is a story about promises and redemption.<br>They were childhood inseparable playmates, but when we said goodbye, they were strangers<br>They don't like each other, but they also attract each other,<br>They are incompatible opponents of fire and water, and they are a perfect match for lovers.</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Characters-</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2773520/extras/d7bdab381e3145cb6e2c9d10e377371a.avif?t=1753181073\" width=500 height=304 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2773520/extras/b0e9cf6e478c819c4169a957b019a492.avif?t=1753181073\" width=500 height=304 /></span><br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>About-</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >着重描写女性之间的微妙细腻感情；</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >纯爱题材，唯一cp，结局的好坏取决于恋爱中的细枝末节；</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >全人物全程配音，体验声入人心的真情对白；</h2><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Staff-</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【制作】xuwule</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【企划】xuwule</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【剧本】selto</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【立绘，cg】大雾</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【背景】诗歌，jancycoco</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【配音】梧枝枝，米糊，沐月幺</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【ui】xuwule</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【pv】xuwule</h2><br>特别感谢：woctordho  鹰仓白霞",
